strings.Value: "Do you know where the 'livemetal' came from?"
"Thanks for the warning. I have to go."
"Warmblood, go careful! Livemetal stand in our way, kill many fellow Longtail."
"Black, scary, make much noise. Spells not hurt it. It can heal itself, very strong."

"It come from a big broken cup. With it come a warmblood shadow, short, in crown, bush of hair on face. Metal is shadow too, I see! They come from past, and want return them kingdom. Bad when dead shadows walk. They want attack us. Longtail arrows kill warmblood shadow. Metal very angry by this."

"Warmblood shadow bring it, look like you — short, strong, in a crown. They come out of big broken cup, say return them kingdom, attack us. But we kill warmblood shadow with arrows. Metal we not kill. Now it very angry."
"I find this — you take. It make black metal not heal. Longtail can not defeat it, but you can!
